											January 1, 2018<br>
										<br>
										
										
										
										
										
											To:<br>
										
										
										
										
										
											All Wanxiang America customers and business partners:<br>
									</b><br>
									Thanks to you, Wanxiang America Corporation is growing, and for better focus on service to you and all of our automotive business partners, we are introducing a slight modification to our internal organizational structure. Wanxiang America Corporation is now comprised of two distinct business units separating our automotive distribution business from other types of businesses (Investments &amp; Holdings, Real Estate, Solar, Healthcare, etc.). This is in the express interest of better service to you.<br>
									<br>
									
									
									
									
									
										Effective January 1, 2018, your business will be served by <b>Wanxiang Automotive Components, LLC,</b> a wholly owned subsidiary of Wanxiang America Corporation. The Wanxiang location, people, phones, fax, email addresses, bank information, etc. all remain the same. <b>Beginning immediately, please address your orders, payments and other correspondence to:<br>
